{{Otheruses|Tibanna}}
'''TibannaX''' was the special isotope of [[Tibanna]] gas used in [[StealthX]]s. The company that produced TibannaX was later purchased by [[Bornaryn Trading]]. Its ion emissions cooled in several milliseconds, making the StealthX hard to track.

